{"version":1,"content":"<html>\n  <body>\n    <p>《PairShot》是一款專為創作者設計的強大攝影 App，目前正推出限時免費活動。對於需要同時捕捉現場實況與個人反應的影音創作者、Vlogger 或是旅遊愛好者來說，這款工具能省去繁瑣的後期剪輯流程，讓你一鍵完成高品質的雙鏡頭拍攝，輕鬆產出適合不同平台的社群影片。</p>\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/460x460bb-75-92.webp\" alt=\"限時免費\">\n    <h2>三種模式自由切換打造完美構圖</h2>\n    <p>提供畫中畫、分屏及單鏡頭自動雙輸出模式。用戶能隨心調整視窗大小與位置，或透過滑動條精確控制各鏡頭縮放。最高支援 4K 60fps 錄製與影片防震功能，並可選擇 MP4 或 MOV 格式儲存。所有錄製完成後會立即存入相簿，無須手動剪輯即可同步產出 9:16 與 16:9 比例的內容。</p>\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/1284x2778bb-130-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"App Screenshot\">\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/1284x2778bb-131-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"App Screenshot\">\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/1284x2778bb-132-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"App Screenshot\">\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/1284x2778bb-133-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"App Screenshot\">\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/2048x2732bb-18-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"App Screenshot\">\n    <ul>\n      <li>應用名稱：PairShot: Dual Camera</li>\n      <li>應用類別：Photo &amp; Video</li>\n      <li>下載位置：App Store</li>\n    </ul>\n  </body>\n</html>","scraped_at":"2026-04-25T09:42:19.464863+00:00","quality":{"score":1,"chars":351,"images":6,"source":"New MobileLife","fallback":"none"}}